{"tid":2443562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社企餐券贈失業青年 每周600元","createTime":"2021-03-12T06:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T09:45:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1599ed72bc28152883e51539c7a3dcbd4a6c14","tid":2443562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/6J64X4HRTRDMZAGY7JNZS3ACZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2F6J64X4HRTRDMZAGY7JNZS3ACZQ%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=53bf324b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2F6J64X4HRTRDMZAGY7JNZS3ACZQ%2F&h=f0d68bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/6J64X4HRTRDMZAGY7JNZS3ACZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n社企餐券贈失業青年 每周600元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fYENu1zFkTUrJZUUnxRoaX8pgkY=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5WWL3AYTNVDAVOFX3MWVCXE2E4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfYENu1zFkTUrJZUUnxRoaX8pgkY%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5WWL3AYTNVDAVOFX3MWVCXE2E4.jpg&h=2e87a835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社區組織CAPcoupon擴展餐券計劃，失業青年可向區議員索取其膳食券。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自去年起，社區組織CAPcoupon與區議員合作，向有需要的在學青年派發膳食券，津貼他們到社區小店用膳，再透過「街坊埋單」形式，讓有心的香港人主動出手認領單據，今年內已經向合資格人士資助超過二萬次膳食。受武漢肺炎疫潮影響，本港的失業率升至近年新高，大量年輕人一畢業就失業。CAPcoupon近日就決定將服務對象擴展至30歲或以下的待業人士，希望能夠幫到更多有需要的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30歲或以下可領取<br />\n<br />\n負責人A（化名）表示，2021年的短短兩個多月內，CAPcoupon已派出二千多張優惠卡，反映不少青年人對生活援助有需要。同時，本港失業率高企，經濟下滑，年輕人就算本身有很高學歷，亦無法找到合適或足夠餬口的長工，只能打散工幫補，甚至要失業。過去亦有負責派發優惠卡的區議員反映，有真正有需要人士因沒有學生證，而失去援助資格。<br />\n<br />\n因此，CAPcoupon決定擴展派發膳食券計劃，由3月15日起，除14歲或以上的在學人士外，30歲或以下受疫情影響而正待業或就業不足的青年，亦可向各區約150名區議員申請援助，每人每星期可獲得一張相等於600元的優惠卡。<br />\n<br />\n受助人可以到全港約400間合作的小店消費，並以優惠卡上的貼紙支付。其他街坊可主動認領張貼出來的有關單據，代受助人「埋單」。<span class=\"orange\">A指，港人反應踴躍，單據張貼一、兩天就很快有港人代為埋單，「支持嘅人仲多過用嘅人」，令人欣慰。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820b234c779ed774dbfbe3e49a4d18c4cb5d231b","tid":2443562,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"34b1385c7e9f0e22f9a195b8706a8445830094f4","tid":2443562,"uid":6352,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"幫後生好重要，政府資源唔會幫後生呢群。"},{"pid":"34ee4c7386544ceb812b1fa5e714e0bb51722640","tid":2443562,"uid":146241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"參加嘅全部都係黃店"},{"pid":"aca655ff3786af8be579e8f28d79a23404ac7e6f","tid":2443562,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"中年呢...."},{"pid":"f3f7070dcb0b325fd89d95203cefbd1f7913857b","tid":2443562,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ab8eba9b3c012c69da35ee05c50a1e255f17a8ef","tid":2443562,"uid":86283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aca655ff3786af8be579e8f28d79a23404ac7e6f","tid":2443562,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"中年呢...."},"citedB